Jean-Paul Rouve https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Paul_Rouve 0 Jean-Paul Rouve (born 26 January 1967) is a French actor, film director, screenwriter and producer. He is a member of the troupe "Les Robins des Bois".He has appeared in more than thirty film and television productions since 1993.
